gomodel:SYNGO_4761  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: AP2B1 was detected in SV biochemical fractions, and enriched as compared to the P2 fraction. This protein was also detected in SV biochemical fractions in Takamori et al. 2006 (PMID: 17110340).. Experimental description: M&M: \"Brain Synaptosomes and SV Purifications. Synaptosomes (P2') and SVs were purified from whole brain of 4- to 6-wk-old Sprague-Dawley rats following the same protocols used in ref. 2 and previously described in ref. 34 for SV, and in ref. 4 for P2'.\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
